tora-san 's lovesick ( 男はつらいよ &lt;unk&gt; otoko wa tsurai yo : torajirō &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1990 japanese comedy film directed by yoji yamada . it stars kiyoshi atsumi as torajirō kuruma ( tora-san ) , and reiko &lt;unk&gt; as his love interest or " madonna " . tora-san 's runaway is the thirteenth entry in the popular , long-running otoko wa tsurai yo series .